<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-55-1049 </DOCNO><TEXT>This volume contains the proceedings of the 8-day conference which reviewsthe state-of-the-art of thick seam technology and the directions fordevelopment. There are 17 papers which discuss the following topics:longwall mining in India and US; longwall technique, strata control;ventilation; rockbursts; computer applications and geomechanics. Allpapers are abstracted separately.</TEXT></DOC>